\n/vol1/@apphome/trim.openclaw/data/workspace/plugins/memory-lancedb-pro/docs/memory_architecture_analysis.md:590:当前需要特别区分两个 recall 路径：\n/vol1/@apphome/trim.openclaw/data/workspace/plugins/memory-lancedb-pro/docs/memory_architecture_analysis.md:592:### auto-recall 路径\n/vol1/@apphome/trim.openclaw/data/workspace/plugins/memory-lancedb-pro/docs/memory_architecture_analysis.md:594:`before_agent_start` 在拿到 recall 结果后会执行完整闭环：\n/vol1/@apphome/trim.openclaw/data/workspace/plugins/memory-lancedb-pro/docs/memory_architecture_analysis.md:602:### `memory_recall` Tool 路径\n/vol1/@apphome/trim.openclaw/data/workspace/plugins/memory-lancedb-pro/docs/memory_architecture_analysis.md:604:`memory_recall` 当前会：\n/vol1/@apphome/trim.openclaw/data/workspace/plugins/memory-lancedb-pro/docs/memory_architecture_analysis.md:611:- Tool recall 会积累访问数据\n/vol1/@apphome/trim.openclaw/data/workspace/plugins/memory-lancedb-pro/docs/memory_architecture_analysis.md:612:- 真正的 tier 迁移维护目前仍只挂在 auto-recall 主链上\n/vol1/@apphome/trim.openclaw/data/workspace/plugins/memory-lancedb-pro/docs/memory_architecture_analysis.md:619:在 auto-recall 生命周期维护中，这类 memory 会被排除在 tier 评估之外，避免会话摘要挤占核心长期记忆层级。\n/vol1/@apphome/trim.openclaw/data/workspace/plugins/memory-lancedb-pro/docs/memory_architecture_analysis.md:623:## 十、读取注入层：auto-recall 的上下文安全模型\n/vol1/@apphome/trim.openclaw/data/workspace/plugins/memory-lancedb-pro/docs/memory_architecture_analysis.md:625:当 `autoRecall === true` 时，`before_agent_start` 会把 recall 结果注入到：\n/vol1/@apphome/trim.openclaw/data/workspace/plugins/memory-lancedb-pro/docs/memory_architecture_analysis.md:641:因此 auto-recall 实际上已经包含：\n/vol1/@apphome/trim.openclaw/data/workspace/plugins/memory-lancedb-pro/docs/memory_architecture_analysis.md:646:- recall 后 lifecycle 驱动\n/vol1/@apphome/trim.openclaw/data/workspace/plugins/memory-lancedb-pro/docs/memory_architecture_analysis.md:678:- `memory_recall`\n/vol1/@apphome/trim.openclaw/data/workspace/plugins/memory-lancedb-pro/docs/memory_architecture_analysis.md