                                    │\n├──────────────────────┼───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┤\n│ Dashboard            │ http://127.0.0.1:40062/app/trim-openclaw/default/                                             │\n│ OS                   │ linux 6.12.18-trim (x64) · node 22.18.0                                                       │\n│ Tailscale            │ off                                                                                           │\n│ Channel              │ stable (default)                                                                              │\n│ Update               │ pnpm · up to date · npm latest 2026.4.2                                                       │\n│ Gateway              │ local · ws://127.0.0.1:40062 (local loopback) · reachable 173ms · auth token · CMCC (192.168. │\n│                      │ 1.113) app 2026.4.2 linux 6.12.18-trim                                                        │\n│ Gateway service      │ systemd not installed                                                                         │\n│ Node service         │ systemd not installed                                                                         │\n│ Agents               │ 5 · 5 bootstrap files present · sessions 16 · default main active 1m ago                      │\n│ Memory               │ enabled (plugin memory-lancedb-pro) · unavailable                                             │\n│ Plugin compatibility │ none                                                                                          │\n│ Probes               │ skipped (use --deep)                                                                          │\n│ Events               │ none                                                                                          │\n│ Tasks                │ none                                                                                          │\n│ Heartbe