{"type":"message","id":"5c9cd1a7","parentId":"5d07aba8","timestamp":"2026-04-05T23:25:38.793Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] 好，直接测，最简单。\n\n你现在发我一条**新的个人偏好或事实**，比如任选一种：\n\n- 我最喜欢的水果是芒果\n- 我常用颜色是深蓝\n- 我周末一般晚起\n- 我不吃香菜\n\n我收到后会：\n1. 先正常回应  \n2. 过一会儿用“绕一点的问法”再验证它有没有被长期记住\n\n如果你想更严格一点，也可以直接发这种格式：\n\n**记住：我最喜欢的水果是芒果**\n\n发一句就行。","textSignature":"{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_0efad9d5f40a5c740169d2ef6f4fe4819aada92f66053aa88c\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}],"api":"openai-responses","provider":"openai","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":32598,"output":139,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":32737,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775431530350,"responseId":"resp_0efad9d5f40a5c740169d2ef6e23b0819a8a69a80c9e246bdc"}}
