{"type":"message","id":"1857960b","parentId":"454e6bf0","timestamp":"2026-04-05T23:35:18.192Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] 这个你**还没告诉过我**，所以我现在不能瞎编。\n\n目前我只确定你提过：\n- 你喜欢喝 **无糖咖啡**\n- 你周末一般 **晚起**\n- 你最喜欢的水果是 **芒果**\n\n如果你愿意，现在告诉我一句：\n**我晚饭后一般喜欢喝××**\n我就可以继续帮你测长期记忆。","textSignature":"{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_06ab4c7d5867edd50169d2f1b1ad20819aadbd604cc8b93f4b\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}],"api":"openai-responses","provider":"openai","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":35565,"output":102,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":35667,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775432109958,"responseId":"resp_06ab4c7d5867edd50169d2f1b0c434819ab1f70490e3973c3f"}}
