{"type":"message","id":"4bc0cafe","parentId":"fca5df42","timestamp":"2026-04-05T23:36:20.172Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] 收到，我记下了：\n\n**你晚饭后一般喜欢喝汤。**\n\n现在你已经给了我 3 条可测试记忆：\n- 你周末一般晚起\n- 你最喜欢的水果是芒果\n- 你晚饭后一般喜欢喝汤\n\n如果你想继续测，下一句可以换个问法，比如：\n- `我晚上一般喜欢喝什么？`\n- `我周末作息怎样？`\n- `我喜欢吃什么水果？`\n\n这样更容易看出到底是短期上下文，还是长期记忆在起作用。","textSignature":"{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_0526a37f834f62550169d2f1e924548198bdc2c043419a88d9\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}],"api":"openai-responses","provider":"openai","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":35738,"output":137,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":35875,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775432164944,"responseId":"resp_0526a37f834f62550169d2f1e80fac8198baf465eee63f2971"}}
